# Akanshya Dash — Personal Website

**Live site:** https://akanshya1998.github.io/My-Website/

This is a personal academic and professional portfolio website 
built with R Markdown and deployed via GitHub Pages.

## What the Site Contains

### Home
A professional introduction including bio, areas of expertise, 
recent research highlights, and contact links.

### Projects
Graduate-level and research projects including:
- Reproducible HIV Epidemiology Pipeline (R, Docker, GitHub)
- Routine Immunization Disruptions & VPD Trends (Capstone)
- HIV Stigma Metrics Repository (Johns Hopkins CHIMES)
- U.S. PrEP Locator Database (PRISM Team, Emory)
- Pharmaceutical Portfolio Strategy (Zydus Lifesciences)

### CV
Full curriculum vitae including education, work experience, 
research projects, skills, and downloadable PDF resume.

## Built With
- R Markdown website framework
- Custom CSS (navy blue theme)
- GitHub Pages for deployment